The paper is about a novel Neu-IR model that visualizes term distribution and handles query-to-document matching at the subtopic and higher levels. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Additionally, the paper uses a neural network model, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), or Computer Vision (cs.CV).
